# Inline Math knowing wether to insert a space afterwards. 
snippet mm "Inline Math" wA
$${1}$`!p
if t[2] and t[2][0] not in [',', '.', '?','!', '-', ' ']:
    snip.rv = ' '
else:
    snip.rv = ''
`$2
endsnippet

# Display Math
snippet dm "Display Math" wA
\[
$1
.\]
endsnippet

